      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/egypt-investment-sentiment-turns-on-interest-rate-hike-devaluation-imf-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两年前几个月内从埃及撤资约 200 亿美元的基金经理现在会发现新兴市场中没有什么地方比这更有吸引力了。]]></description>
