    <item>
      <title>随着金价飙升，中国黄金热度已连续第 16 个月增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/china-s-gold-splurge-reaches-16th-month-as-prices-hit-record</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国央行2月份连续第16个月增加黄金储备，延续了长期购买热潮，帮助支撑贵金属飙升至历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/china-s-gold-splurge-reaches-16th-month-as-prices-hit-record</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 08:26:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在欧洲央行做出决定之前，欧洲股市保持在创纪录水平；诺沃跳跃</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/european-stocks-ease-from-record-as-focus-turns-to-ecb-decision</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股市在创下历史新高后几乎没有变化，因为投资者转向法兰克福寻找欧洲央行利率路径的线索，央行可能会保持借贷成本稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/european-stocks-ease-from-record-as-focus-turns-to-ecb-decision</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 08:14:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚保持关键利率稳定以支撑令吉疲软</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/malaysia-leaves-key-rate-unchanged-amid-ringgit-weakness</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚周四维持基准利率不变，延长了观望立场，因为政策制定者在通胀和经济增长风险迫在眉睫的情况下应对货币走弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/malaysia-leaves-key-rate-unchanged-amid-ringgit-weakness</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 07:00:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大陆集团在市场放缓的情况下面临严峻的汽车部门改革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/continental-sees-rising-margins-after-savings-in-auto-business</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2021 年 10 月 25 日星期一，德国法兰克福的大陆集团汽车工厂。第三季度半导体短缺和其他供应链问题加剧，进一步扰乱汽车制造后，大陆集团下调了全年销售额和利润指引。摄影师：亚历克斯·克劳斯/彭博社]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/continental-sees-rising-margins-after-savings-in-auto-business</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 06:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着日本利率押注的增加，股市暂停，日元飙升：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球股市在历史高点附近暂停，而日元则飙升，因为人们越来越相信日本央行最终将在三月份开始加息，这是最后一个这样做的主要央行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 22:49:47 GMT</pubDate>
